			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">i guess it goes w/out saying that dot crits, damage avoidance/mitigation are great and should be continued.  
<br />

<br />
coming from a low aa'd player, i like the pet upgrade aas, they add some dps that continues to work as we increase in levels, which is always nice.  
<br />

<br />
the aas that increase crit damage would probably be a good line to continue, i haven't actually started working on them yet, i'm still lvl 70 and working on the last available crit dot aas atm.
<br />

<br />
the gift of mana line is really nice, maybe something to make these trigger slightly more often, or as an expendable aa, something like 1 aa to give yourself a 25% increase in trigger rate for a 10 min period or something, would be really useful for just about any situation
<br />

<br />
thats all i can think of atm, haven't really gotten too much into the other aa lines, so i don't really want to comment on swarm pets or anything like that
